### Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}